on button-down \'93Activate\'94 ( or A key ) send to each unit prefab its string \'93unit_id_input\'94 then send event \'93activate_instance\'94 to each unit prefab, important that the unit prefab receives the string before sending the event. This will set the unit prefab and their values according to their id in the database\
\
Each prefab then send to scene.cs message \'93OnActivateButtonClicked\'94 when the values are pulled from the database into the local variables of each unit prefab so the UI knows it can display the sliders\
