scene.cs activates the UI displaying the sliders to set tweak the values of each unit, that will modify in real-time the values of the variables in the selected unit\
\
on UI  button-down \'93Start\'94 ( or S key ) send to each unit prefab event \'93start\'94 and to scene.cs message \'93OnStartButtonClicked\'94 so the action starts\
\
